query:
UPDATE feeds
      SET url = $1,
          name = $2,
          private_key = $3,
          public_key = $4,
          image_url = $5,
          icon_url = $6,
          title = $7,
          description = $8,
          site_url = $9,
          error = $10,
          updated_at = $11,
          hashtag = $12,
          content_warning = $13,
          status_publicity = $14,
          admin = $15,
          listed = $16,
          error_count = $17,
          tweaked_profile_data = $18
      WHERE id = $19
